    {
      "id": 164298,
      "category": "researcher",
      "content": "I was able to achieve Cache Deception and/ Poisoning to Cloudflare Customers who were using `Cache Deception Armor` Software using `.avif` extension file\n\n\nThis required User interaction, hence the severity set to Medium\n\nSeverity varies, it depends on what the customer was exposing in their responses\n\n e.g.\n\nIf the customer had user's session within the response, Account Takeover was possible\n\nIf I was able to find a XSS on the customer website, Stored XSS was possible\n\n\n\n\n",
